1
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,600
Princess,

2
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:51,400
conditions are

3
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,330
a bit rough here.

4
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,820
But please don't mind.

5
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:56,640
Once we find the Copper Frog,

6
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,720
we'll enjoy ourselves properly.

7
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,360
By then,

8
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,560
hotpot, beer,

9
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,610
SPA and massage,

10
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,210
I'll arrange it all.

11
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:06,490
I don't understand.

12
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:07,800
But

13
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,280
I didn't expect you to have

14
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,810
such a luxurious carriage.

15
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,200
Carriage?

16
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,440
What carriage?

17
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,680
You mean...

18
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,000
this is a high-end,

19
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,840
luxury SUV.

20
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,400
When the sun rises,

21
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,440
we shall meet again.

22
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,240
Goodnight.

23
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,440
Liu Yu,

24
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,970
what's going on over there?

25
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,060
Professor Wei,

26
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:00,800
listen to me.

27
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,760
The person who entered the virtual space with me,

28
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,280
she's in my car right now.

29
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:05,000
And

30
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:08,210
she says she'll take me to find the third copper frog.

31
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,680
That's too much of a coincidence.

32
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,960
Don't get scammed.

33
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,280
We just found

34
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,120
the second copper frog.

35
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:15,880
How can there be clues

36
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,210
to the third one so soon?

37
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,400
The AI hasn't even upgraded yet.

38
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,480
That makes sense.

39
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,560
Wait, no.

40
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:25,480
She knows a lot of things.

41
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,560
She knows the location of the copper frog,

42
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,760
and she knows many things

43
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,240
not recorded in history books.

44
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,120
That doesn't mean anything.

45
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,480
It's easy to fake that.

46
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,940
Just make sure you don't get scammed.

47
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,200
Long time no see.

48
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,120
What was that about just now?

49
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,560
She's the one I've been looking for.

50
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,640
She would never lie to me.

51
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,440
I trust her.

52
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,040
Very confident.

53
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:04,920
I get it.

54
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,360
You're a typical case of

55
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,240
raging male hormones.

56
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,720
You can fake anything.

57
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,920
But the feeling of meeting someone,

58
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,050
that can't be faked.

59
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,640
Listen.

60
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,800
You old bachelor.

61
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,600
You'll never understand.

62
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,399
When she told me,

63
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,920
from the moment she said "See you tomorrow,"

64
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,880
I wished immediately

65
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,240
that the sun would rise and set,

66
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,760
and dawn would come in the blink of an eye.

67
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,560
I even wished that in the next moment,

68
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,760
she and I would have already grown old together,

69
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:32,080
sitting in rocking chairs hand in hand,

70
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:34,320
surrounded by our grandchildren.

71
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,890
I think you're just being ridiculous.

72
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,680
Someone of unknown origin,

73
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,800
and you trust her this much?

74
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,460
Did someone put a spell on you?

75
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,610
Are you even listening?

76
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:45,440
Hello?

77
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,320
Liu Yu,

78
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,640
listen to me.

79
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,240
No.

80
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:56,000
Someone is using me.

81
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,280
I think I know who it is.

82
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,640
Only he knows

83
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,500
I'm looking for Buluotuo's Tear.

84
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,920
And only he

85
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:07,060
could do something like this.

86
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:15,720
Hello?

87
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:16,920
Listen to me.

88
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,260
Liu Yu is in danger.

89
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,960
I need you to do whatever it takes

90
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,760
to save Liu Yu.

91
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,920
Keep me posted.

92
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,040
Okay, I got it.

93
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,800
I'm on my way.

94
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,580
(Thai) What are you doing?

95
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,300
I don't have time to play with you.

96
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,650
Maybe we'll meet again.

97
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,530
(Thai) You know where they are?

98
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,000
I'll say hello to your girl

99
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,400
for you.

100
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,000
Bye-bye.

101
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:38,770
(Thai) Wait.

102
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,800
(Thai) If I offended you before,

103
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,340
please forgive me.

104
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:52,520
(Thai) Aya is really important to me.

105
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:56,000
She doesn't have much time left.

106
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,920
I want to take her to the best doctor.

107
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:01,280
I want her last moments

108
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:03,000
to be happy.

109
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,120
I think

110
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,560
she's pretty happy

111
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,960
being with Liu Yu.

112
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,080
(Thai) Please, take me with you.

113
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,160
I don't care about the Bronze Frog

114
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,560
or the Tears of Buluotuo.

115
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,080
I just want to get my Aya back.

116
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:25,920
I didn't expect you to be such a romantic.

117
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,120
Get in.
